Generate new report project in Visual Studio
Generate new report in the report project
Open the new report with the Design/Preview and Report Data
Make sure the SQL Server instance is added to Visual Studio
Add the SQL Server to the Data Source by entering the server name from SSMS inin Build window (in data source property)
Select or enter the desired database name into the same window
Add Dataset embedded in report with query.
Insert table in the Design and drag desired fields into the table and Preview
Right click the project or report in Visual Studio to build and then Deploy
Check report in Preview and in Report Service Or Report Portal window
